  | accessdate = 2007-02-22 }}</ref> A listening party event for the album took place on July 22 at Duff's Brooklyn in Williamsburg, New York.<ref name="SLAYER: 'Christ Illusion' Listening Party Scheduled For This Weekend">{{cite web
  | title = SLAYER: 'Christ Illusion' Listening Party Scheduled For This Weekend
