  | accessdate = 2007-02-22 }}</ref> [[BBC Radio 1]]'s "Mike Davis Rock Show" gave "Skeleton Christ" a premier airing on August 1,<ref name="SLAYER: 'Skeleton Christ' Track Available Online">{{cite web
  | title = SLAYER: 'Skeleton Christ' Track Available Online
  | author =  
  | publisher = [[Blabbermouth.net]]
  | date = [[2006-08-03]]
  | url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=55968
  | accessdate = 2007-02-22 }}</ref> and by August 4 the full album was available for streaming via Slayer's official [[MySpace]] profile.<ref name="SLAYER: Hear 'Christ Illusion' In Its Entirety">{{cite web
  | title = SLAYER: Hear 'Christ Illusion' In Its Entirety
